skins.selfIntroduction: I'm the Royal Navy M-class destroyer Musketeer! I was in the Battle of the North Cape! Commander, little Musketeer is gonna shoot straight through your dreary heart with a bang bang!
skins.acquisition: I am the M-class Destroyer, Musketeer! Hehe... I knew something good was going to happen today~ Commander, can you point me to where the port is? Here? Or over here?!
skins.login: Morning, Commander! Nice weather today! Click, click... bang! I'm not sure why, but I'm always brimming with energy!
skins.details: Is it fun to hang out with me, Commander? ...Ah, sorry, never mind that.
skins.secretaryIdle1: Something nice is gonna happen today~ That's what I'm feeling!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Why am I always smiling? Hehehe, because I've been having so much fun ever since I came here!
skins.secretaryIdle3: The injuries I've sustained from combat? Hehehe, they don't hurt at all.
skins.secretaryTouch: Hehehe~! You've reloaded me with energy!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: It's not like I *dislike* it, but... Yeah, I actually don't dislike it!
